<plot>The Good Samaritan is the strange saga of Neil Gulbert - an oddly obsessive and idealistic campaign volunteer for local town mayor Stan Fong. One fateful morning Neil receives an offer from Fong's office to work side by side with his beloved Mayor. Neil is placed on a strict time deadline to get to campaign headquarters and secure the job of his dreams. With destiny a short walk away, Neil sets out on foot. On his bizarre crosstown journey, Neil encounters a series of citizens in potential danger. Overcome by an unwavering and compulsive need to help these people, and with time ticking away, Neil feels he must first save his town, one person at a time, all in the name of Mayor Fong.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?561615</url></doc>
